<inglise> Whereas Regulation (EC) No 820/97 establishing a system for the identification and registration of bovine animals and regarding the labelling of beef and beef products stipulates that the system for identification and registration of bovine animals is to include eartags to identify animals individually, computerised databases, animal passports and individual registers kept on each holding; </inglise>
