<inglise> Where on-the-spot checks conducted in accordance with Article 6(5) of this Regulation reveal infringements of Regulation (EC) No 820/97, copies of the reports of the on-the-spot checks pursuant to this Regulation shall be sent without delay to the authorities which are competent for the implementation of Regulation (EC) No 2630/97. </inglise>
<eesti> Kui vastavalt k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;ruse artikli 6 l&otilde;ikele 5 tehtud kohapealse kontrolli k&auml;igus selgub, et on rikutud m&auml;&auml;rust (E&Uuml;) nr 820/97, saadetakse k&auml;esolevale m&auml;&auml;rusele vastava kohapealse kontrolli aruande koopiad viivitamata m&auml;&auml;ruse (E&Uuml;) nr 2630/97 rakendamiseks p&auml;devale asutustele. </eesti>
